{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/TIL_41_210215/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"63-loggin-the-user-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#63-loggin-the-user-in\" aria-label=\"63 loggin the user in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[6.3] Loggin the User In</h1>\n<h3 id=\"what-to-learn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-to-learn\" aria-label=\"what to learn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>what to learn</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>db에 유저 정보를 저장하는 것(<code class=\"language-text\">User.register()</code>)에서 한단계 더 나아가, </li>\n<li>User를 authenticate 하고 로그인 시킴</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"1-passportauthenticate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-passportauthenticate\" aria-label=\"1 passportauthenticate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. passport.authenticate</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>앞선 <code class=\"language-text\">postJoin</code>에서 넘겨받은 user의 eamil, passport 정보를 바탕으로 등록 유저 여부를 auth</li>\n<li>\n<p>공식 문서 : <a href=\"http://www.passportjs.org/docs/authenticate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://www.passportjs.org/docs/authenticate/</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const postLogin = passport.authenticate(&#39;local&#39;, {\n  failureRedirect : routes.login,\n  successRedirect : routes.home\n})\n}</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-passport를-시작시키고-전체에-다-넘겨준다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-passport%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B3%A0-%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%A4-%EB%84%98%EA%B2%A8%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"2 passport를 시작시키고 전체에 다 넘겨준다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. passport를 시작시키고, 전체에 다 넘겨준다</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>app.js에 아래 코드 삽입</p>\n<ul>\n<li>import passport from \"passport\"</li>\n<li>import \"./passport\" : passport 만들어진 파일을 연결</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-appjs에-아래-코드-삽입--passport를-시작시키고-session에-쿠키-정보를-담음\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-appjs%EC%97%90-%EC%95%84%EB%9E%98-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85--passport%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B3%A0-session%EC%97%90-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EB%8B%B4%EC%9D%8C\" aria-label=\"3 appjs에 아래 코드 삽입  passport를 시작시키고 session에 쿠키 정보를 담음 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. app.js에 아래 코드 삽입 : passport를 시작시키고, session에 쿠키 정보를 담음?!</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>passport를 사용한 곳에는 다 passport를 import 해줌 </li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">app.use(passport.initialize())</code></li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">app.use(passport.session())</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>이걸 위해서 <code class=\"language-text\">express-session</code> install 필요 -> 자세한 기능은 다음 강의에서 배우자!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-localmiddleware에-있는-user정보-변경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-localmiddleware%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-user%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"4 localmiddleware에 있는 user정보 변경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. localMiddleware에 있는 user정보 변경</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">req.user</code>안에, 로그인/조인 하는 유저 정보가 담긴다. 때문에 이 정보를 담아줌</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"6.3 Loggin the User In what to learn db에 유저 정보를 저장하는 것()에서 한단계 더 나아가,  User를 authenticate 하고 로그인 시킴 1. passport.authenticate 앞선 에서 넘겨받은 use…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#63-loggin-the-user-in\">6.3 Loggin the User In</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#what-to-learn\">what to learn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#1-passportauthenticate\">1. passport.authenticate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#2-passport%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B3%A0-%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%A4-%EB%84%98%EA%B2%A8%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\">2. passport를 시작시키고, 전체에 다 넘겨준다</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#3-appjs%EC%97%90-%EC%95%84%EB%9E%98-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85--passport%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B3%A0-session%EC%97%90-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EB%8B%B4%EC%9D%8C\">3. app.js에 아래 코드 삽입 : passport를 시작시키고, session에 쿠키 정보를 담음?!</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_41_210215/#4-localmiddleware%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-user%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\">4. localMiddleware에 있는 user정보 변경</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/TIL_41_210215/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TIL-210215","date":"Feb 15, 2021","tags":["TIL","userauthentication","passport"],"keywords":["dobedh","Donghyun Kim"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/TIL_41_210215/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-02-15"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}